arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(tCocoonedVillagers[idActorGizmo]) then
		
		idLastSavedVillager = tCocoonedVillagers[idActorGizmo]
		Hydra.ActorRemoveFromPrefabScopedGroup(idLastSavedVillager, PSAG_WEBBED_VILLAGERS)
		tCocoonedVillagers[idActorGizmo] = nil
		Hydra.ActorSetInvisible(idLastSavedVillager, false)
		
		Hydra.EventSendToActor("AdvancePhase", ID_THIS_QUEST, ID_THIS_QUEST)

		if Hydra.PrefabScopedActorGroupGetCount(PSAG_WEBBED_VILLAGERS) > 0 then 
			Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONV_FREED, idLastSavedVillager) 
		end
		
		Hydra.QActorAnimAndNewIdle(idLastSavedVillager, ANIMKEY_SICK_PRONE_GETUP, ANIMKEY_NEUTRAL)
		
	else
	
		local spawn
		if Hydra.GetRandomInt(1, 2) == 1 then
			spawn = GetRandomTableEntry(T_RANDOM_SPAWNS)
		else
			spawn = Hydra.ActorPickFromEncounter(GetRandomTableEntry(T_RANDOM_ENCOUNTERS), ID_THIS_QUEST)
		end
		Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(
			spawn, 
			Hydra.PositionSnapToGround(Hydra.ActorGetPosition(idActorGizmo)), 
			Hydra.ActorGetFacing(idActorGizmo), 
			false, 
			0, 
			0)
	end
	
	cocoonOpened(idActorGizmo)
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	--No super elite if a villager dies.
	if SUPER_SPAWNS == true then
		SUPER_SPAWNS = false
	end
end

function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)

	if not Hydra.ActorIsArchetype(idActorSpawned, "mini") then
		Hydra.ActorMergeAIState(idActorSpawned, STATE_KILL_PREY, idActorSpawned, 0)
		Hydra.ActorAddToPrefabScopedGroup(idActorSpawned, PSAG_SPIDERS)
	end
	
	
end

function Start(flTimeRemaining)
	if SUPER_SPAWNS == true then
		if Hydra.PrefabScopedActorGroupGetCount("LE_Spider_Elite") == 0 then
			Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(SUPER_SPAWNER)
		end
	end
end

arQuestPhases.szOnEnterScript:
Hydra.Wait(1)

Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONV_WARNING, idLastSavedVillager)
Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(CONV_WARNING)

Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_THIS_QUEST, SFX_WAVE_MINOR)

for i, idVillager in pairs(Hydra.ActorsInPrefabScopedGroup(PSAG_VILLAGERS)) do
	Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idVillager, false)
	Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idVillager, true)
	Hydra.ActorMergeAIState(idVillager, AISTATE_FLEE, idVillager, 0)
end

for i, spawnerID in pairs(T_SPAWNERS) do
	Hydra.ActorEnable(spawnerID)
end

for i, cocoonID in pairs(T_COCOONS) do
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(cocoonID) then
		cocoonOpened(cocoonID)
	end
	
end

for i, spawnerID in pairs(T_SPAWNERS) do
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(spawnerID) then
		Hydra.ActorDelete(spawnerID)
	end
end
arQuestPhases.szOnExitScript:
for i, idVillager in pairs(Hydra.ActorsInPrefabScopedGroup(PSAG_VILLAGERS)) do
	Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idVillager, true)
	Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idVillager, false)
	Hydra.ActorRemoveMergedAIState(idVillager, AISTATE_FLEE)
end

arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start()

	local sChest = ACTOR_CHEST_REWARD

	if Hydra.QuestGetBonusPhaseResult() then
		sChest = ACTOR_CHEST_REWARD_HEROIC
	end
	
	Events.SpawnRewardChest(CHEST_LOCATION, sChest)

	local idSpeaker = GetRandomTableEntry(Hydra.ActorsInPrefabScopedGroup(PSAG_VILLAGERS))
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idSpeaker) then
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONV_VICTORY, idSpeaker)
	end

end

szUserFunctionsScript:
local function GetRandomTableEntry(t)
	return t[Hydra.GetRandomInt(1,#t)]
end

local function IsNearAnotherCocoon(pt, tSpawnPoints)
	
	local nSpawnPoints = #tSpawnPoints
	
	if nSpawnPoints <= 0 then 
		return false 
	end
	
	for i=1, nSpawnPoints do
		if Hydra.PositionGetDistanceToPosition(pt, (tSpawnPoints[i])) < 4 then
			return true
		end			
	end
end

local function cocoonOpened(idActor)
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(idActor, POWER_SPAWN_MINIS)
	Hydra.ActorKill(idActor)
	Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(idActor, 2)
end
szOnStartupScript:
ID_THIS_QUEST = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()

PSAG_COCOONS = "LE_Hatchery_Cocoons"
PSAG_SPAWNERS = "LE_Hatchery_Spawners"
PSAG_SPIDERS = "LE_Hatchery_Spiders"
PSAG_VILLAGERS = "LE_Hatchery_Villagers"
PSAG_WEBBED_VILLAGERS = "LE_Hatchery_Webbed_Villagers"

SUPER_SPAWNS = true

T_ANIMSETS = {ANIMSET_WOUNDED, ANIMSET_WOUNDED_ARM, ANIMSET_WOUNDED_HEAD}

T_RANDOM_SPAWNS = 
	{
	Hydra.ReferenceActor("Generic_Corpse_Horse_Part_Head_Any_1x1_01_Arrangement"),
	Hydra.ReferenceActor("Generic_Corpse_Horse_Part_Leg_Any_1x1_01_Arrangement")
	}

T_RANDOM_ENCOUNTERS =
	{
		ENCOUNTER_CORPSE,
		ENCOUNTER_BLOATED_CORPSE
	}
	
T_COCOONS = {}
	
local T_ACTOR_COCOONS =
	{
		ACTOR_COCOON_GIZMO_01,
		ACTOR_COCOON_GIZMO_02,
		ACTOR_COCOON_GIZMO_03,
		ACTOR_COCOON_GIZMO_04,
		ACTOR_COCOON_GIZMO_05
	}

local T_SPAWN_PTS = {}

local PT_THIS_QUEST = Hydra.ActorGetPosition(ID_THIS_QUEST)
local PT_FACING_THIS_QUEST = Hydra.ActorGetFacing(ID_THIS_QUEST)

local N_COCOON_MIN = 7
local N_COCOON_MAX = 9
local N_VILLAGER_COUNT = 3

for i=1, Hydra.GetRandomInt(N_COCOON_MIN, N_COCOON_MAX) do
	
	local ptSpawn = Hydra.PositionSearchForNearbyNavmeshPosition(PT_THIS_QUEST, 0, 9)
	
	for i=1, 50 do
		if IsNearAnotherCocoon(ptSpawn, T_SPAWN_PTS) then
			ptSpawn = Hydra.PositionSearchForNearbyNavmeshPosition(PT_THIS_QUEST, 0, 9)
		else
			break
		end
	end

	ptSpawn = Hydra.PositionSnapToGround(ptSpawn)
	T_SPAWN_PTS[#T_SPAWN_PTS+1] = ptSpawn
	
end

Hydra.Wait(1)

for i=1, #T_SPAWN_PTS do
	local idCocoon = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(
		GetRandomTableEntry(T_ACTOR_COCOONS),
		T_SPAWN_PTS[i],
		PT_FACING_THIS_QUEST,
		true,
		0,
		0)
	T_COCOONS[#T_COCOONS+1] = idCocoon
	Hydra.ActorAddToPrefabScopedGroup(idCocoon, PSAG_COCOONS)
end

tCocoonedVillagers = {}

for i=1, N_VILLAGER_COUNT do

	local idLastCreatedActor = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(
		Hydra.ActorPickFromEncounter(ENCOUNTER_NPC, ID_THIS_QUEST), 
		T_COCOONS[i], 
		true, 
		0, 
		0)
	
	Hydra.ActorSetIdleAnim(idLastCreatedActor, ANIMKEY_SICK_PRONE)
	tCocoonedVillagers[T_COCOONS[i]] = idLastCreatedActor
	Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idLastCreatedActor, true)
	Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idLastCreatedActor, false)
	Hydra.ActorSetInvisible(idLastCreatedActor, true)
	Hydra.ActorAddToPrefabScopedGroup(idLastCreatedActor, PSAG_WEBBED_VILLAGERS)
	Hydra.ActorAddToPrefabScopedGroup(idLastCreatedActor, PSAG_VILLAGERS)
	Hydra.ActorSetAITether(idLastCreatedActor, ID_THIS_QUEST)
	
	Hydra.ActorSetAnimSetOverride(
		idLastCreatedActor, 
		T_ANIMSETS[Hydra.GetRandomInt(1, #T_ANIMSETS)],
		false)

	end
	
	for i, actorID in pairs(Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(ID_THIS_QUEST, "initialSpiders")) do
		Hydra.ActorMergeAIState(actorID, STATE_IDLE, actorID, 0)
	end
